L.HelpText: Add a directory to the library search path
L.Name: L

Map_eq.HelpText: Print a link map to the specified file
Map_eq.Name: Map=

allow_undefined.HelpText: Allow undefined symbols in linked binary. This options is equivelant to --import-undefined and --unresolved-symbols=ignore-all
allow_undefined.Name: allow-undefined

allow_undefined_file.HelpText: Allow symbols listed in <file> to be undefined in linked binary
allow_undefined_file.Name: allow-undefined-file=

check_features.HelpText: Check feature compatibility of linked objects (default)
check_features.Name: check-features

compress_relocations.HelpText: Compress the relocation targets in the code section.
compress_relocations.Name: compress-relocations

error_limit.HelpText: Maximum number of errors to emit before stopping (0 = no limit)
error_limit.Name: error-limit=

export_dynamic.HelpText: Put symbols in the dynamic symbol table
export_dynamic.Name: export-dynamic

export_eq.HelpText: Force a symbol to be exported
export_eq.Name: export=

export_if_defined_eq.HelpText: Force a symbol to be exported, if it is defined in the input
export_if_defined_eq.Name: export-if-defined=

export_table.HelpText: Export function table to the environment
export_table.Name: export-table

features.HelpText: Comma-separated used features, inferred from input objects by default.
features.Name: features=

gc_sections.HelpText: Enable garbage collection of unused sections
gc_sections.Name: gc-sections

global_base.HelpText: Where to start to place global data
global_base.Name: global-base=

growable_table.HelpText: Remove maximum size from function table, allowing table to grow
growable_table.Name: growable-table

import_table.HelpText: Import function table from the environment
import_table.Name: import-table

import_undefined.HelpText: Turn undefined symbols into imports where possible
import_undefined.Name: import-undefined

initial_memory.HelpText: Initial size of the linear memory
initial_memory.Name: initial-memory=

l.HelpText: Root name of library to use
l.Name: l

max_memory.HelpText: Maximum size of the linear memory
max_memory.Name: max-memory=

no_check_features.HelpText: Ignore feature compatibility of linked objects
no_check_features.Name: no-check-features

no_entry.HelpText: Do not output any entry point
no_entry.Name: no-entry

no_export_dynamic.HelpText: Do not put symbols in the dynamic symbol table (default)
no_export_dynamic.Name: no-export-dynamic

no_gc_sections.HelpText: Disable garbage collection of unused sections
no_gc_sections.Name: no-gc-sections

no_pie.HelpText: Do not create a position independent executable (default)
no_pie.Name: no-pie

no_print_gc_sections.HelpText: Do not list removed unused sections
no_print_gc_sections.Name: no-print-gc-sections

no_whole_archive.HelpText: Do not force load of all members in a static library (default)
no_whole_archive.Name: no-whole-archive

o.HelpText: Path to file to write output
o.Name: o

print_map.HelpText: Print a link map to the standard output
print_map.Name: print-map

reproduce_eq.HelpText: Dump linker invocation and input files for debugging
reproduce_eq.Name: reproduce=

stack_first.HelpText: Place stack at start of linear memory rather than after data
stack_first.Name: stack-first

thinlto_cache_dir.HelpText: Path to ThinLTO cached object file directory
thinlto_cache_dir.Name: thinlto-cache-dir=

thinlto_cache_policy_eq.HelpText: Pruning policy for the ThinLTO cache
thinlto_cache_policy_eq.Name: thinlto-cache-policy=

thinlto_jobs.HelpText: Number of ThinLTO jobs. Default to --threads=
thinlto_jobs.Name: thinlto-jobs=

threads_eq.HelpText: Number of threads. '1' disables multi-threading. By default all available hardware threads are used
threads_eq.Name: threads=

trace.HelpText: Print the names of the input files
trace.Name: trace

unresolved_symbols_eq.HelpText: Determine how to handle unresolved symbols
unresolved_symbols_eq.Name: unresolved-symbols=

version.HelpText: Display the version number and exit
version.Name: version

whole_archive.HelpText: Force load of all members in a static library
whole_archive.Name: whole-archive
